name: FÉMINA - ESPEJO FÉMINA
description:
This is the final chapter of a timeline in which we have been travelling.
With the beatiful hand of @D_Mogeon, we saw a sort of redemption for all women. A promise of a better tomorrow, the possiblity to write a new chapter, a different story.
No queríamos quedarnos en el enojo y en la desidia de lo que hemos transcurrido, si no honrar ese universo que llevamos dentro.
We, women, are mirrors, clovers, the soul of the whole creation.
